  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skolly's Adventure is a small, single-player adventure game, in which you play as Skolly, a skeleton adventurer and treasure hunter ! travel the world on your flying boat, explore various strange environments, solve puzzles and collect all the shiny things ! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features : </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573930/extras/a3304258f9bf05afd0c84eb0643b9e91.poster.avif?t=1762323139\" width=622 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573930/extras/a3304258f9bf05afd0c84eb0643b9e91.webm?t=1762323139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573930/extras/a3304258f9bf05afd0c84eb0643b9e91.mp4?t=1762323139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 10 floatings islands with unique environements to discover ! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573930/extras/436dec13df9da20eaca22c790e09141f.poster.avif?t=1762323139\" width=622 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573930/extras/436dec13df9da20eaca22c790e09141f.webm?t=1762323139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573930/extras/436dec13df9da20eaca22c790e09141f.mp4?t=1762323139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 60 Levels to complete and Treasure to collect ! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573930/extras/c50b98389752a611c3c1770e0562c299.poster.avif?t=1762323139\" width=622 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573930/extras/c50b98389752a611c3c1770e0562c299.webm?t=1762323139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573930/extras/c50b98389752a611c3c1770e0562c299.mp4?t=1762323139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 10 Colors to find and customise Skolly's apearence !  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >This Game Is Perfect For :</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > everyone in need of a calm game, mainly focus on exploration !  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > everyone who like solving puzzles and collecting things !  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > everyone looking for short game that can be completed a few hours ! </p></li></ul>",
